of different services,

00:19:43.090 --> 00:19:46.780
including Feedly, which is what
we have hooked up here.

00:19:46.780 --> 00:19:50.830
But the idea is that it's
basically a client your

00:19:50.830 --> 00:19:53.450
reading stuff, your
reading queue.

00:19:53.450 --> 00:19:56.120
I would call it the
pre-Pocket.

00:19:56.120 --> 00:19:58.095
You look at something here, and
maybe if you want to read

00:19:58.095 --> 00:19:58.910
it later, you throw
it into Pocket.

00:19:58.910 --> 00:19:59.504
ADAM KOCH: That's definitely
my workflow,

00:19:59.504 --> 00:20:01.360
like press to Pocket.

00:20:01.360 --> 00:20:02.080
ROMAN NURIK: Yeah.

