But the idea here--

00:20:03.450 --> 00:20:06.140
the reason we like this app so
much is that it's just very

00:20:06.140 --> 00:20:07.740
clean, again, very minimal.

00:20:07.740 --> 00:20:09.400
It's all about content.

00:20:09.400 --> 00:20:10.310
You can even look here.

00:20:10.310 --> 00:20:12.770
The tabs here on the left--

00:20:12.770 --> 00:20:14.970
actually, on a phone,
this would be one

00:20:14.970 --> 00:20:16.300
screen here on the left.

00:20:16.300 --> 00:20:18.510
And this would be
the next screen.

00:20:18.510 --> 00:20:20.550
We basically have tabs
here on the left.

00:20:20.550 --> 00:20:25.950
And the icons for the tabs
are incredibly minimal.

00:20:25.950 --> 00:20:28.810
The filled circle means
that it's unread.

00:20:28.810 --> 00:20:31.890
