means it's read.

00:20:31.890 --> 00:20:34.920
And the star just means it's
your starred content.

00:20:34.920 --> 00:20:37.630
So it's a very interesting
workflow.

00:20:37.630 --> 00:20:40.590
You basically have your step
one, you have stuff that you

00:20:40.590 --> 00:20:41.140
haven't read.

00:20:41.140 --> 00:20:44.370
Step two is the next evolution
of that, stuff you've read.

00:20:44.370 --> 00:20:46.085
And step three is stuff that
you really care about and

00:20:46.085 --> 00:20:46.490
you've starred.

00:20:46.490 --> 00:20:48.680
So the hierarchy there
is very clear.

