great on Android.

00:24:17.680 --> 00:24:20.590
Specifically, there are some
character spacing things that

00:24:20.590 --> 00:24:22.750
come up with fonts that
aren't optimized.

00:24:22.750 --> 00:24:26.090
So "New York Times's" font here
is specifically optimized

00:24:26.090 --> 00:24:30.060
